```

1. `compliance/vendors.md` — full internal inventory (all data, all scoring, all renewal dates).
2. `compliance/vendor-risk-{YYYY-Q}.md` — quarterly review snapshot (executive summary).
3. `compliance/sub-processors/CURRENT.md` — public-facing sub-processor list (only data classified for external sharing).

